input.command: sqlite3 "/Users/david/workspace/claude-code-claimdb/test_dbs/california_schools.sqlite" "SELECT s.Phone, sat.sname, CAST(sat.NumGE1500 AS REAL) / sat.NumTstTakr AS excellence_rate, sat.NumGE1500, sat.NumTstTakr FROM satscores sat JOIN schools s ON sat.cds = s.CDSCode WHERE sat.NumTstTakr > 0 AND sat.NumGE1500 IS NOT NULL ORDER BY excellence_rate DESC LIMIT 10;"

All three phone numbers match exactly what the claim states, in the correct order.
